"np91":[null,"At 100 nM activity is already 15% — well past 50% inhibition. The IC50 must be lower.","Activity drops below 50% by 50 nM. An IC50 above 500 nM would mean the drug barely works.","IC50 is interpolated between data points. It rarely falls exactly at a tested concentration."],
